                    "type": "EXPERIMENTAL",
                    "description": "For their tonsil surgery, subjects will receive Dexmedetomidine (1mcg/kg bolus given intravenously at induction of anesthesia) and Acetaminophen (12.5mg/kg with a maximum dose of 1 gram given intravenously at induction of anesthesia). Ketorolac 0.5mg/kg with a max dose of 30mg given intravenously at the end of surgery. No opioids will be given during the procedure.",
